# EXAMPLES

Run and plot the *Test_SX* example (Single crystal diffraction)
:   - `@MCCODE_PREFIX@run Test_SX.instr -d output_dir -n 1e7 TTH=13.4`
:   - `@MCCODE_PREFIX@plot-svg output_dir`

